# Agent Configuration
# This file is tracked by git and serves as the bootstrap pointer for AI agents.
#
# Framework Location:
#   Workflows: .agent/workflows/
#   Rules:     .agent/rules/
#   Templates: .agent/templates/
#
# Maintained Workflows:
#   - setup-new-game.md    : Initialize new game test environment
#   - setup-load-game.md   : Load existing game save
#   - game-round.md        : Run one round of game generation
#   - sync-private.md      : Backup agent config to private repo
#   - test.md              : Run linting and type checks
#   - plan.md              : Feature planning template
#
# Private Backup: https://github.com/michael2221807/ming_private.git
#   To sync changes: Run .agent\scripts\sync-to-private.bat
#
# CRITICAL RULES:
#   - File imports require USER manual action.
#   - If data is lost, STOP and ask the user to re-import.
#   - API keys must be entered by the user.
